<item>
            <title>[LU-8275] ssk: add flag to test suite to enable ssk for tests</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8275</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Chris Hanna and I have been working on getting single shared key working with the test suite. When the SHARED_KEY environment variable is set to 1, test-framework will set up a shared key between the nodes and start Lustre with shared key enabled. Then tests can proceed as per usual. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
